      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. DEADLY STING turned in yet another strong performance last time when he battled on bravely to just miss out over 1609m at this track, adding to a string of recent minor placings. Beautifully placed and is sure to be there at the finish. 6. SEVEN LICK IMAGE finished fifth last start, beaten 24 metres at this track over 1609m. Has ability and should be right in the finish. 7. EIGHTY PLUS EIGHTY can break his way into the winner's list after registering a sequence of four top-three finishes, the latest at this track a week ago. 1. MONIVON MILLSTREAM is at the track for the first time. By Ready For Moni and hails from the Daren Harvey stable. No excuses from this advantageous draw. Makes plenty of appeal.\",\"runners\":[5,6,7,1],\"exclusive\":false}",
